# Deployment Entity
deployment: |md
  **Deployment**

  Fields:
  - id: UUID
  - model_id: UUID
  - environment: string
  - endpoint_url: string
  - deployment_type: DeploymentType
  - status: DeploymentStatus
  - created_at: timestamp
  - updated_at: timestamp
  - config: JSON
  - health_check_url: string
  - scaling_config: JSON
  - monitoring_config: JSON
  - rollback_model_id: UUID
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#1a1a2e"
  style.stroke: "#3fb950"
  style.font-color: "#e6edf3"
}

# Lineage Entity
lineage: |md
  **Lineage**

  Fields:
  - id: UUID
  - parent_type: EntityType
  - parent_id: UUID
  - child_type: EntityType
  - child_id: UUID
  - relationship_type: LineageType
  - created_at: timestamp
  - metadata: JSON
  - version: int
  - operation: string
  - operator: string
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#1a1a2e"
  style.stroke: "#3fb950"
  style.font-color: "#e6edf3"
}

# Relationships
feature -> lineage: tracks usage
model -> training_run: produces
training_run -> model: creates version
model -> deployment: deployed as
deployment -> lineage: records deployment
training_run -> lineage: records training
lineage -> feature: references
lineage -> model: references
